1. Create a new Restaraunt - This api should be used to create a new restaraunt. The information regarding the input json is provided below.

URL: http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/restaraunt/create
Method: PUT
Headers: Content-type - "application/json"
Request Body:
{
  "sid": null, //Not required
  "id": null, //Not required
  "email": "hotel1@test.com",
  "description": "description",
  "photoUrl": "hotel_url", // The photourl provided by the hotel
  "name": "Hotel Test HNagar", //Hotel Name
  "primaryContact": "9898657898", //The contact number for the hotel
  "createdDate": 1453321422902, //long value of the current ssytem date
  "address": "Address 1", //
  "pin": "560102",//PinCode - mandatory
  "latitude": "12.912408", //Double value -- Mandatory
  "longitude": "77.633957", //Double value -- Mandatory
  "costFor2": 45, //Integer - mandatory
  "area": {
    "sid": "86B5BCD2CA374479B41DF5E41A1BE5A649A23E8462FB4D5D93C59E960EB80176",
    "id": null,
    "areaName": "New Area"
  },//This part will be provided when the user select an item from the "area" dropdown
  "active": true //Default value
}

2. Get List of area - This api should be used to get the list of area for a city and it should be used to populate the "area" dropdown for the above requirement.

URL: http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/restaraunt/areas/city/9AF4BF308C9B4E6CBB3F75D7B674D0E90224E75C7426410B9CA18B55E4E24D12
Method: GET
Response JSON- This will be Json array
[
  {
    "sid": "9AF4BF308C9B4E6CBB3F75D7B674D0E90224E75C7426410B9CA18B55E4E24D12",//This is the area SID 
    "id": null,// Not exposed to external
    "areaName": "JP Nagar",//Name of the area
    "city": {
      "sid": "9AF4BF308C9B4E6CBB3F75D7B674D0E90224E75C7426410B9CA18B55E4E24D12",
      "id": null,
      "cityName": "Mysuru"
    }
  }
]

3. Generate order report for a restaraunt - This api provides a list of all the orders placed for a particular restaraunt between two dates. This has pagination support from the server side.

URL: http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/order/orders/<restaraunt_sid>
Method: POST
Headers: Content-type - "application/json"
Request Body:
{
    "fromDate":1453321422000,//The from date from where the report should be generated
    "toDate":1453321422000,// The to date till where the report should be generated
    "count":10, //The result count for each page -- If complete result set is required then pass 0
    "pageIndex":1 //This is the pageIndex, always starts with 1
}

ResponseBody:
[
  {
