4. List of restaraunt - This api will provide the list of restaraunt based on the area sid provided. The list of restaraunt will be used to populate a drop down in the admin UI from where the user can select a particular restaraunt. This feature will be required for the API # 3

URL - http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/restaraunt/search
Method: POST
Headers: Content-type - "application/json"
Request Body:
{
  "areaSid": "9AF4BF308C9B4E6CBB3F75D7B674D0E90224E75C7426410B9CA18B55E4E24D12",// the area sid as fetched from #2
  "stateSid": null,//Not required
  "timings": "BR"//Keep this value hard-coded
}
 Response JSON:
 [
	{
      "sid": "F0E2C8E8924541CEA7FC8B9A18A086CBCE1D2ACE1A704CFF9021457739B97255",// Restaraunt Sid
      "id": null,
      "name": "Hotel Test RRR",
      "primaryContact": "9898657898",//Not important for this API
      "address": "RRR,Gandhi Square, Near Mahatma Gandhi Statue, Chamrajpur, ",//Not important for this API
      "pin": "570001" //Not important for this API
    }
 ]

5. Update the delivery status - This API should be used to update the delivery status of an Order. The delivery statuses are PLACED which is default and is always set when order is placed. OFD - Out for delivery and DEL - Delivered when the order gets delivered. The user must be able to select any of the last two options to update the delivery status

URL: http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/order/status/<order_sid>/<status>
Method: POST
Headers: Content-type - "application/json"

6. Update the payment status for an order -  This api should be used to update the payment status of an Order payment. The statuses are 		S
		STARTED, -- Default set by server
		PENDING, -- This is also determined and set by server
		COMPLETED, -- This is the option that a user can select because incase of Online payments this will be set by the server.
		PENDING_CONFIRM --  This is also used for internal server purpose

URL: http://<domain-name>/restaraunt-rest-0.0.1.local-SNAPSHOT/rest/order/payment/status/<payment_sid>/<status>
Method: POST
Headers: Content-type - "application/json"

